Apple of the Eye"

In the world of K-pop, there are many stars, But one shines brightest, in your eyes. Le Sserafim, the apple of the eye, His light illuminates the path.

You are a true fan, With unconditional love, without fear. Le Sserafim is your passion, Your apple of the eye, forever.
